<br>
Yes, click nuke items are a lot larger intervals of upgrades. Whereas a melee would upgrade their damage slightly over time, mages upgrade in large spurts by getting clicky nukes. If you're concerned about that so much, I have some advice: get over it. Click nukes will never scale appropriately through all levels of play.<br>
<br>
It's not like they can go back now and make burst damage good. Most casters can all but chain nuke already anyway, because the game has been redesigned as it evolved, with insane mana regen &amp; insanely efficient spells. <p>Happy trails.</p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=krilenspiritlink>Krilen Spiritlink</A> at: 11/29/02 6:29:49 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=cydmab>Cydmab</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Sage</span><br>  Posts: 677<br> <font color=#333333>(11/29/02 7:09:25 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=7965.topic&index=69>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_question_mark.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Is 200dps sustained Possible?</span><hr size=1> OK, from a 6 hour, 21 minute log in crypt of decay, EQ companion estimates 4 hours 15 minutes, 27 seconds of combats. Total damage from my nukes was 952,500; cast ancient 783 times, blazing heat 472 times. DPS was 62.1. Now this includes alot of &quot;dead time&quot; including fights where I only cast one nuke because of positioning, afking, fireshielding, confusion, etc. Pulls were almost constant; I went out of my way to pet canabilize and I only did it 80 times in over 6 hours. I had tranquility, SoA (sometimes down because of rods), 15 FT, XPG, and rodded regularly. I was using summoned bracer, lightbringer's ear, and boots of the wind. I had blessing of retribution on me about half the time. I was using pendant of malosini to malosini most mobs (needed for resits, and to help pet)<br>
