<br>
From the time we noticed the add until the time the first mob died, my nuking dps was 82.  This is more than double my average output.<br>
<br>
Normal group dps was something like (rogue105, War 70, unknown wizard (guessing 35.. wiz had kei but used root), 90 mage). Guessing on a 20k hp mob, but at 300dps the 20k mob should die in about 67 seconds.  Add my 42dps burst damage, and the fight is shortened to 59 seconds.<br>
<br>
Remember we have a wizard using root as crowd control here...  Suppose I was ignoring burst dps ability and just going along at 90dps instead of 132, root broke 60 seconds into the fight, and in the 7 seconds it takes us to finish off the primary target the wizard dies.  Bam several thousand mana's worth of potential damage down the toilet.<br>
<br>
