Furthermore, it becomes harder to maintaim uptime as you kill more mobs.  The true measure of a group's accomplishment is the which mobs they were able to kill and how many.  Increasing your uptime is a goal, to be sure, but is not in itself a measure of how good a group is. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=goladus>Goladus</A> at: 11/30/02 12:04:21 pm<br></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.showMessageRange?topicID=7965.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.showMessageRange?topicID=7965.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.showMessageRange?topicID=7965.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a> <b>4</b> <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.showMessageRange?topicID=7965.topic&start=81&stop=100>5</a><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.showMessageRange?topicID=7965.topic&start=101&stop=101>6</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.showPrevMessage?topicID=7965.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.showNextMessage?topicID=7965.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=7965.topic&index=80><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.threadControl?topicID=7965.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/unread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerge